              <tr><td><strong>Growth PMM</strong></td><td>In-product messaging, onboarding</td><td>Activation flows, feature adoption campaigns</td><td>PLG motion, freemium product</td></tr>
              <tr><td><strong>Technical PMM</strong></td><td>Developer/API product</td><td>API documentation, integration guides</td><td>Developer-facing products</td></tr>
            </tbody>
