              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>No. Product marketing specialises in positioning, messaging, and go-to-market strategy. General marketing encompasses brand, demand generation, events, and broad campaigns. Product marketing is the bridge between product, sales, and marketing — ensuring all three speak with one voice.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
