          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">How is product marketing measured?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Metrics include competitive win rates, launch pipeline impact, sales content usage rates, conversion rates from leads to closed deals, analyst perception scores, and share of voice. Gartner research finds companies with dedicated PMMs achieve 15-20% higher win rates.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
