            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Product marketing defines what to say and to whom. Content marketing produces the assets that say it — blog posts, case studies, comparison pages, videos. Product marketers brief content teams on messaging and positioning; content teams execute those briefs into published assets.</p></div></div>
